column5: Hoping my first three fish pulled thru a hole this season is an omen of a great season ahead.   First fish of the season,         Second fish of the season,      My 3rd fish coming from the hole            Hopefully this is an omen to my future outings!
Those are beauties!
That pickerel's a brute !!
Nice Specks, and beauty Walleye
Wow! Excellent fish. As Lew said, that pickerel IS a brute  but those specks are really close to my heart. Congrats to you Mike.
great way to start
Nice fish!!,WTG.What a start !!!
very nice!
Great way to start 2015!
Awesome fish pix!  Thanx  That wally is a tank!
Man those are beauties.  Hope they keep coming.
Great way to start the season.
Nice start to the season! Love the jaw on the first Speck
Awesome start to your season Mike! Those specks are just "speck-tacular!" Well done all around, tight lines!
Wow !!!! Awesome fish ..... That eye is a tank !!!
Beauty fish! The pressure is off now! If I didn't get another fish through the ice all season after those, I'd still be happy!
Nice fish
Considering I don't believe that walleye is a Quinte fish Mike, it's super impressive!  But the trout are equally as good.
Wow, great fish - everything else this season will just be gravy!
Wow, here hoping my first fish of the season will be half that size lol!
Fantastic specks and an absolute hawgasaurus walleye!  You're off to a better start than most!
You don`t piddle around with the small guys eh, just straight to the tanks  Very impressive!
Wow, nice fish bud, the pickerel is huge, way to go!!!!!
Nice catch Mike, WTG.
Very Jealous here...sitting on my hump waiting for ice sucks lol...
